title: War of the Roses - I Had To Chase An Owl
description: Max called the show today to see if his girlfriend, Stephanie, is cheating. She was late for lunch and she's NEVER late. She told him that she had to chase an owl out of her house. Didn't take pics / videos so he's a little suspect of it. Plus more red flags so we'll figure out what's going on!
